{"tid":2295851,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（感情台x 學術台） 求偶市場價值","createTime":"2020-11-22T05:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T09:35:02.000Z","uid":374778,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"014dc78388e89f527863f2e7657cf7d6c1122fc2","tid":2295851,"uid":374778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:19:54.000Z","msg":"點解溝唔到女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解無人要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊用理性角度分析愛情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，男係demand，女係supply。<br />\n由於需求大過供應<br />\n市場價格會提高（出現擇偶條件）<br />\n女方因此會揀擇男嘅，釣高黎買。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，男方求偶市場價值最高嘅時間，俾女方來得遲。<br />\n男方求偶市場價值最高嘅時候大概30-40歲<br />\n係事業開始有成之時<br />\n女方求偶市場價值最高嘅時候大概15-25歲<br />\n係最青春嘅時侯<br />\n<br />\n第三，男女結婚，好多時都係雙方求偶市場價值一樣（市場平衡點）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位，即使你依家係A0，唔好太擔心<br />\n你只係未搵到equilibrium姐"},{"pid":"99dadd16519a8e93b56aba3837ce3e99ff48e634","tid":2295851,"uid":374778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"利申：毒撚，求偶市場價值係0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea00aad17187877b79f8bf5497d508f52e52166b","tid":2295851,"uid":370010,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"637c92b88cd6538292624216756cbd7f911c6eea","tid":2295851,"uid":308492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:05:40.000Z","msg":"套理論咁熟<br />\n係咪日本仔講過嘅戀愛資本主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e351e0a245042812e375edb855c463a12d68ff23","tid":2295851,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99dadd16519a8e93b56aba3837ce3e99ff48e634","tid":2295851,"uid":374778,"like":0,